                In cooperation with us, you can get transportation from China to Southeast Asia, the Middle East, India, Africa, North America, and Europe to Russia. Delivery is possible "from door to door". To receive cargo, Baltic and European ports and warehouses are used. </ P>
                <br/>
                <p> SeaLines develops a logistics chain and delivers goods "from door to door" starting from the stage of documentation formation and ending with the unloading of the container in your warehouse. </ p>
                <br/>
                <p> Our company provides a wide range of services. Becoming our partner, you will have opportunities that other companies will not be able to provide to you. With our help, you can: deliver your cargo, forget about the design of documentation, about port services and other factors. Also, the company SeaLines offers its partners to increase their capital. One of the activities of the company is that we can offer you a sublease / lease / lease with the right to purchase a container for which a logistics chain has already been established, loading it with a more profitable product. You still have to track your container online. We also provide a convenient option for the customer to buy-back. </ P>
                <br/>
                <p> We consider it our mission to save your time, make your product competitive and optimize transportation costs. We help to transport cargo from anywhere in the world easily and quickly, without any unnecessary hassle and expense. <br/>
                We have won the trust of our customers by offering optimal solutions for the transportation of goods and eliminating any errors related to the human factor. <br/>
                Container shipping by sea is the best, in some cases even the only variant of intercontinental cargo delivery. Reliable and economical. </ P>
                <br/>
                <ul> Advantages of sea transportation: <br/>
                    <li> - The low cost of shipping by sea is largely due to the possibility of picking up groupage cargoes. </ li>
                    <li> - high carrying capacity, in the case of large-sized cargoes, the transportation of containers by sea often becomes not only the best, but also the only possible option for delivery. </ li>
                    <li> - the safety of the cargo during the transportation of containers by the sea is almost non-existent - the risk of cargo damage is minimal.
                    Sea Lines Company is a notable player in the container market in Europe, the Baltics, Russia and the CIS. We specialize in containers of the widest range of types, dimensions and purpose - dry cargo or universal (sea) containers, refrigerated containers (referrals), tank containers, specialized containers, etc. In addition, we supply and establish auxiliary equipment for containers: generator sets (gensets), etc. </ li>
                </ ul>
                <br/>
                <p> SeaLines Company has been operating in the container market for more than 5 years, and the high level of understanding of the business needs of customers achieved over the years helps to quickly and efficiently solve all issues related to the use of containers for multimodal transport and warehousing of all types of cargo. We provide our clients with ready-made and customized solutions for transportation, logistics, construction and any other activities where containers are used. </ P>
                <br/>
                <p> For more than 5 years SeaLines Company has been providing high reliability and security of container service for its customers. We vouch for the confidentiality and safety of the goods during transportation and storage (in particular, in the protected area adjacent to the port area). </ P>
